@startuml posterior-fusion
' Neural emission posteriors fused into the WFST decoding graph.
' AcousticModel::forward emits per-frame log-posteriors P(unit∣frame); FusionConfig
' weights them against the LM score inside the recognition network N = H∘C∘L∘G;
' the weighted product is searched (Viterbi/beam) to yield words.
' Matches AcousticModel / FusionConfig / AcousticLanguageModel in src/acoustic/mod.rs.
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam ArrowColor #6A1B9A
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.4
skinparam rectangle {
  RoundCorner 12
  FontColor #102027
  BorderColor #E65100
}

title <b>Neural posterior fusion into the decoding graph</b>\n<size:11>combined = λ_am · log P(unit∣frame) + λ_lm · log P(word∣context) + penalties</size>

rectangle "<b>Audio frames</b>\n[T × feature_dim]" as X #ECEFF1
rectangle "<b>AcousticModel</b>\nneural net · forward()" as AM #E1BEE7
rectangle "<b>Posteriors</b>\nlog P(unit∣frame)\nFramePosterior / PosteriorSequence" as POST #E1BEE7

X  -down-> AM  : features
AM -down-> POST : per-frame log-probs

rectangle "<b>Recognition network N</b>\nH ∘ C ∘ L ∘ G   (unit → word)" as N #FFB74D
rectangle "<b>FusionConfig</b>\nλ_am · acoustic_weight\nλ_lm · lm_weight\nword/blank penalties" as FUSE #FFE0B2

POST -down-> FUSE : λ_am · log P(unit∣frame)
N    -down-> FUSE : λ_lm · log P(word∣context)

rectangle "<b>Search</b>\nViterbi / beam over  posteriors ⊗ N" as DEC #C8E6C9
rectangle "<b>Words</b>" as W #ECEFF1

FUSE -down-> DEC : weighted product
DEC  -down-> W

note right of FUSE
  Scores live in a log-domain semiring (LogWeight), so
  the fused product is a semiring ⊗ and alternative paths
  combine with ⊕. AcousticLanguageModel::to_log_weight
  packages the result as a WFST arc weight.
end note
@enduml
